FBIS3-16931 "drsov055_b_94017" FBIS-SOV-94-055 Document Type:Daily Report 21 Mar 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin Decrees Local Self-Government Elections LD2103183594 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1546 GMT 21 Mar 94 LD2103183594 Moscow ITAR-TASS Language: English Article Type:BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent] [Text] Moscow March 21 TASS -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin issued a decree allowing regional authorities to announce elections to local self-government bodies for Autumn, the press service of the Russian leader said on Monday. "The decree says that bodies of state power of the subjects of the Russian Federation taking into account local conditions can announce elections to legislative bodies of local self-government for Autumn 1994", the press service said.
